snippet.title: Doom 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Doom 2 (aka doom ii: hell on earth), Dos PC game produced by id Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/doom-2/247/
First epic stage, killing first level zombies faced in my way. Then, the second stage I was not so lucky.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
The Ultimate Doom - https://youtu.be/deF6pC7lc4Y
Quake - https://youtu.be/_ts3gVC1AFY
Duke Nukem 3D - https://youtu.be/puKmt1eZElM
